plot: Frank prepares for his promotion to Vice President. Doug tries to erase all leads leading back to him and Frank. Claire fights back against Gillian. Zoe considers working with Frank again.

Claire decides to go to court with Gillian, while plotting against her. Francis chooses his replacement. Doug and Francis arrange Rachel's departure. Meanwhile, Zoe, Lucas and Janine keep looking for Rachel and trying to expose the cover-up of Russo's arrest. Claire gives up trying to get pregnant. Zoe says yes to starting working again for Francis but makes a massive discovery in the process—Andreea D
